I"d<p>This is a demo at the most basic level for creating an API in Node using the <a href="https://expressjs.com/">Express</a> framework.</p>

<p>You will need node and npm to run this. My preferred option is via <a href="https://brew.sh/">Homebrew</a>. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">brew install node</code> should then give you node and npm. Use <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">node -v</code> to verify.</p>

<p>To create our required packake.json file: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">npm init</code>.
To install Express locally: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">npm install express --save</code>.</p>

<p>Enjoy!</p>

